Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭亡之前的Deus还留下“核”图谋续命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个的话应该维持到7月28日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是我的仆人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该无法随意使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有双手上的圆环压制着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时候来临之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是在特等席看戏比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替你统治这个走向灭亡的世界的人将会是老朽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆鲁姆鲁是也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:17.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:22.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:25.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:30.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:41.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:53.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:06.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:07.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:12.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:18.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:24.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界会在7月28日毁灭？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的手机预知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小雪的日记上应该也能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\an5\fs25\pos(433,224)}世界毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\an5\fs25\pos(591,309)}小雪死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\an5\fs25\pos(641,355)}我也和他一起死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就28号了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28日不止是这样哦 小雪
