Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是最重要的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:59.16,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}翻译 小舌 校译 洛艾妖 时间 仓鼠 后期 DK  压制 克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz-3\pos(475,62)}小雪和由乃结合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小雪结合的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}不履行契约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs28\an5\pos(412,287)}三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前来的时候我记得电和水都被停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是自己又连上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正世界就要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所有都会完结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在泡澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起泡吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 是泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定以为我什么都没穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎 小雪的假话很容易被看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等哦 我现在就重新烧水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡是每天都要洗的哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的持有人已经都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用担心会被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人不能复活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能大家才是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎的是由乃才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她为什么要说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也想杀掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存游戏的赢家只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃怎么会杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\fs28\pos(429,378)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs25\frz13\pos(641,145)}[我妻家 厨房前]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs25\frz12\pos(703,164)}由乃在厨房叫我。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(660,200)}好像有什么事情要我过去。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(672,230)}[我妻家 厨房前]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(445,340)}由乃邀我一起泡澡。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(644,329)}[我妻家 院子]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\pos(491,422)}由乃和往常一样在劈柴。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是在怀疑由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是继续检查日记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着把你塞进爸爸的浴衣里看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 今天一起去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等… 这个有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泡澡的时候不带着日记太不谨慎了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是个只懂杀戮的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我或许没什么魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等全部结束了 我以为你会爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪却完全不把我当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为这样 才邀我一起洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃她是说喜欢我…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却想杀我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃真的想杀掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会的话 明明随时可以杀掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么面对由乃才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄不明白自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次跟你讲话是在教室里呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃只剩下小雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃都会一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看着小雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\frz3\pos(581,143)}[我妻家 房间里]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\frz3\pos(584,164)}由乃在被子前等我。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(584,184)}[我妻家 房间里]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(473,209)}和由乃结合。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(449,253)}由乃说“今天是人生中最棒的一天”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(588,267)}[我妻家 房间里]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(427,295)}世界毁灭。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an5\frz3\pos(516,310)}由乃也死了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是世界完结的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明由乃一直在注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看着由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道她的真实想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在所剩无几的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好爱着由乃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把7月28日的HAPPY END
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前一天实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\an5\frz12\fry5\pos(597,136)}小雪和由乃结合。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs25\frz12\fry5\an5\pos(597,136)}小雪和由乃结合。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁身子还暖着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到被窝里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃才是 什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要温柔点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 就像小宝宝一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然绕了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从最开始就觉得应该会是这种结局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 由乃 跟我说真话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么骗我说爸爸和妈妈可以复活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也想杀掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你成为神的话大家就可以复活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想鼓励小雪 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算成为神也不能让大家复活这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚开始参加游戏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从Deus那里知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以杀了我吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然杀了由乃我也许就能成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样的话 由乃也不能复活不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小雪可以活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得杀掉由乃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要变成神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和由乃一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又这么说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我的疑问就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了秋濑君那条奇怪的信息之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出常理的信息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 秋濑君的手机里写着由乃的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是由乃曾经变成过神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间是从未来倒回的“第二周的时间”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…至少今天一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和小雪一起幸福地度过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先从这里逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还是那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(417,266)\c&HADB1AF&}问卷调查“将来的梦想”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\c&HADB1AF&\pos(492,368)}四点之前交上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你也写不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周爸爸和妈妈离婚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然触摸不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆鲁姆鲁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是你和2nd的 过去的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候2nd已经把自己的父母杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要和我一起去看星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来的梦想什么的根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予2nd希望的并非他人 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来成为你未来的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们都变成大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么2nd想要杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要看啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看啊 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 别看啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里存在的是过去到未来的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个影像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样啊 姆鲁姆鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责就是让游戏变得更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是即兴表演而已 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次给你们介绍我未来的丈夫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃把我当做精神支柱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd的梦想就是成为你天野雪辉的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 反正是无法实现的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后生存游戏就开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后剩下的只能是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 2nd很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样下去和天野雪辉在一起的时间就会有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过游戏的最后必须要有一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉 你想怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让一切归零的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为神 让大家复活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让由乃幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经知道这一切都无法实现的如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想自杀的话 那被2nd杀了也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在进入正题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“第一周的世界”是如何结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一周？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋濑没告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看这些影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 这和我知道的过去有点差别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才给你看的是“第一周的世界”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在实际上是活在“第二周的世界”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二周？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一周的1st和2nd打倒了所有持有者而存活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后选择了殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后就是2nd的第一步的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我哦 天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为神 让你复活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}醒过来啊 怎么不醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能恢复身体 但却无法召回灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一周的2nd还不知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃不是问了Deus 然后知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 她根本就没问过Deus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她实际试过之后才知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际试过才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得控制时间和空间的力量的2nd许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回到原来的雪辉所在的以前的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是第二次的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迈向的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要两个我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是2nd最怕你知道的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 现在存在的由乃是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到过去的 进行第二周的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三具尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是原来就在这个世界的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被自己杀掉了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人不都是自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 醒醒啊由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是过去的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法触摸也不能干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时说要成为我的新娘的 不是这个由乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被自己给杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声…音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了天野君的…声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:32.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどのぐらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:32.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还将失去几何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:38.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動を許される
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:38.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份悸动才将被允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:43.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　焚くって涙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:43.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 焚烧之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:49.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　降れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:49.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 如将滑落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来の繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都为紧系未来之锁匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:23:02.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる体に傷目感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:23:02.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于崩坏之身中觉察那心伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:11.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度　君を　守ると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:11.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将再次 守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:14.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:14.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关雪辉的事找我商量准没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样 我对男女之事很是通透
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问 如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.57,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内啥 真心抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这不科学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.65,0:24:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该是这种展开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 淡定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经准备好下一套方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么方案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.46,0:24:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 快给我跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.37,0:24:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真乃不科学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为年轻人都好这口的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是不是对女人没兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非first他……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:24:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由乃想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.35,0:25:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
